{"type": "article", "id": 36364, "title": "露华浓重组，以及，\"恭喜发财\"球鞋你要来一双么 |  浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-01-04T02:51:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 6822, "name": "kinfolk"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 35531, "name": "三叶草"}, {"id": 36432, "name": "客制球鞋"}, {"id": 13154, "name": "露华浓"}, {"id": 36433, "name": "J.C Penney"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170104093757bl6wMcuCrJpGinVs.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/revlon-restructures-elizabeth-arden-acquisition-10736617/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>露华浓开展 2017 业务重组</b></a> | 去年九月，美国化妆品牌 Revlon 露华浓曾收购了 Elizabeth Arden。为了精简收购后的公司架构，露华浓宣布正式展开 2017 业务重组计划，该计划将在 2020 年之前，在全球范围内裁员 350 人，斥资 6500-7500 万美元。于 1 月 3 日起，正式通知受此影响的员工。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2017/01/03/jcpenney-headquarters-debt/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为减轻债务压力，J.C Penney 要出售它的总部</b></a> | 美国大型百货连锁 J.C Penney 在周二宣布，要以 3.53 亿美元的价格，出售它位于德克萨斯的总部，但是会租回其中的 65%，用作办公空间。公司的首席执行官 Marvin Ellison 称，此举是为了减轻 J.C Penney 的债务压力。截止至 2016 年 10 月 29 日，J.C Penney 有 45 亿美元的长期债务。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>本土创意工作室<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/01/03/air-jordan-4-the-remade-400ml-chinese-ny/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 400ml 携手球鞋客制单位 The Remade，打造全新 Air Jordan 4\"恭喜发财\"定制套装</a>，除了成人尺码球鞋外，还特别增加了 2-6 岁的儿童尺码可供选择。这双鞋延续了中国红的主调，选用了荔枝皮搭配高级植绒皮，看起来还挺喜庆的。据称，每双鞋都要花费 20 个小时手工制作，这个套装还包括高工艺木盒、“发”字方巾和主题插画等配件。配套发售的还有“恭喜发财”主题的连帽卫衣和圆领卫衣。该系列将于 1 月 8 日正式登陆 Kaffiend 、Dunk.com.cn、INXX 等指定零售商。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100456hArZ6IzNHpL2dSbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655109\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100508NRQfEBlnJ408ajCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100508WJXBfah2ykVrItQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100508DJpOjx7QZCsE4KNw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100508sm6LOpCHDBYMRlJo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100519EsrMJPVugW3z15d0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655109\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100519gxFh0rDwaBz1HIJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100519meKRCDbGHTwZpL9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100528mS7sIDzeJhld26a4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100528cuby45q6VePmZFIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/prada-invites-you-to-play-dress-ups/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 发布 2017 早春系列</a>，灵感来自现代游牧民族。高饱和度的尼龙色彩加上大面积混搭印花，令人耳目一新。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100426KcRi3bnGCPuHqxAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100426piO264h3PqNRkCIa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100436X2YWV3TR0o6haE5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701041004361dvtO8jUemlSbBEZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701041004439mygdSbE6C1j2Kka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Reebok 最近几年也会在中国的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/reebok-instapump-fury-2017-cny\" rel=\"nofollow\">农历新年推出特别版鞋款</a>。今年的生肖款以经典款式 Instapump Fury 为原型，鞋身则用了仿鸡毛处理，鞋跟处还加入了中国刺绣图腾，拉环位置绣上了“正”字图，寓意鸡年是第十个生肖年。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701041004086qR7HyfCY4TgwUXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100408qS1AWuYzCmNO834M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701041004163VgyvrXRZhLDWC5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100416lZzJeF5LOgShIjYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">摄影师 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/aaron-tilley-kyle-bean-kinfolk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aaron Tilley 联同艺术家 Kyle Bean，为《Kinfolk》杂志拍摄了一组相片</a>，利用镜头捕捉了一些事件发生前的瞬间，比如鸡蛋掉落在瓷砖上、墨水滴落在 衬衫上等，给读者留下了充分的想象空间。</font></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100335dOLKVnwMtYWIf5go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100344FXoc6jUz5NIaJZhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100344ZvuNAkaqipx0sbMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100344SkavguX9Cy0q6rJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100352Hm3Vol1NFZSdyibv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">之前我们介绍过 adidas Originals 的鸡年限定系列宣传片。这次，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2017/1/adidas-originals-ultraboost-cny-energy-eqt\" rel=\"nofollow\">三叶草推出了米色的，搭载 BOOST 鞋底的 CNY Energy EQT 鞋款</a>。其鞋跟处的公鸡图案，鞋身的仿鸡毛材质和麻雀挂饰，以及麻将元素的鞋垫。鞋盒的设计也别出心裁，特意选用富怀旧色彩的绒面内里木箱，并于木箱角落上雕刻公鸡图案。这双鞋将于 1 月 24 日登陆香港，售价为 2500 港币。&nbsp;</p><p></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701041002598OQ1LqSZR6x7fUar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100259540vcxNRZKGMtnTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100307Z5PeCadI7hmrBnVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100313517uw0ocpLgitWRv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100314ScBOiuQ2hn43tbZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100313lwazB9k4dbXNvCg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170104100319kBIJ6MfTQEA0XwGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/01/03/air-jordan-4-the-remade-400ml-chinese-ny/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}